 first work to evaluate the\nperformance of state-of-the-art transmit diversity scheme under hostile jamming\nattacks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Apr 2020 16:25:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 May 2020 12:17:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-05"}
