. The stability of the relaxed bilayer\nat the first magic angle is estimated to be of the order of 0.5-0.9 meV per\natom (or 7-10 K). Our calculations shed light on the importance of an accurate\ndescription of the vdW interaction and of the resulting atomic relaxation to\nenvisage the electronic structure of this really peculiar kind of vdW bilayers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Apr 2020 16:47:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-28"}
