cal parameters for the positivity of the cell-averaged void fraction and\npartial densities. The positivity of the cell-averaged solution is extended to\nnodal values by the use of an a posteriori limiter. The high-order accuracy,\nnonlinear stability, and robustness of the present scheme are assessed through\nseveral numerical experiments in one and two space dimensions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Apr 2020 18:34:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-17"}
