forcement and policy-makers. Follow-up studies needed to confirm long-term\ntrends may be affected by the COVID-19 pandemic that drastically changed\nsocietal conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Apr 2020 18:37:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-09"}
