nCOVID-19 effectively with only a small number of COVID-19 annotations.\nExtensive experiments verify the effectiveness of COVID-DA and its great\npotential for real-world applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Apr 2020 03:13:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-05"}
